        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I often find that I am writing a block of code like this to get a parameter and validate it.\n{noformat} \n    $default = 0;\n    $validator = new Zend_Validate_Digits();\n    if (false === ($validator->isValid($this->_getParam('parameter', $default)))) {\n       $param = $default;\n    }\n{noformat} \nBeing able to do this would be much nicer:\n{noformat} \n    $param = $this->_getParam('parameter', 0, new Zend_Validate_Digits());\n{noformat} \nI will attach a patch to allow this to work. \nIf this is wanted I will provide tests.\n"
        },
